thread.title: Lane Kiffin looks absolutely miserable in awkward FAU promo
thread.title_full: Lane Kiffin looks absolutely miserable in awkward FAU promo

author: Sara Harris (sharris@sportingnews.com)
title: Lane Kiffin looks absolutely miserable in awkward FAU promo
text:
January 31, 2017 4:16pm   3:59pm EST Lane Kiffin doesn't seem too excited to be coaching at Florida Atlantic University. Lane Kiffin   4:16 p.m. ET 
Updated at 4:16 p.m. ET 
Lane Kiffin doesn't seem too excited to be coaching at Florida Atlantic University. 
The former Alabama offensive coordinator didn't even crack a smile in FAU's promo for National Signing Day. Commit to the Owls! Coach @Lane_Kiffin is bringing in the best recruits. Now we need the best fans!
